OL,7,FThe LPC will also be required to put
OL,8,Fforward "recommendations on achieving
OL,9,Fa single adult rate in the years
OL,10,Fahead".
OL,12,FChancellor Rachel Reeves said: "To
OL,13,Fensure the right balance is struck
OL,14,Fbetween the needs of workers, business
OL,15,Faffordability and the wider economy,
OL,16,Fthe LPC is being asked to consult on
OL,17,Fseveral issues before recommending the
OL,18,Fnew rates."
