OL,7,FLast year, Labour committed to
OL,8,Fremoving these age bands to create a
OL,9,F"genuine" national living wage, as
OL,10,Fpart of efforts to bolster employment
OL,11,Frights.
OL,13,FCurrently, the national living wage
OL,14,Ffor workers aged 21 and older is
OL,15,F#12.21.
OL,17,FMeanwhile, the minimum wage for
OL,18,Fworkers aged between 18 and 20 is #10.
