OL,7,FThe LPC, which was founded in 1997,
OL,8,Fprovides recommendations to the
OL,9,FGovernment each October regarding how
OL,10,Fit believes the minimum wage should be
OL,11,Fchanged.
OL,13,FThe Government ultimately sets minimum
OL,14,Fwage rates for the following April
OL,15,Fafter this advice.
OL,17,FBusiness Secretary Jonathan Reynolds
OL,18,Fsaid: "Low pay drags down living
OL,19,Fstandards for our workers and in turn
OL,20,Fhurts our high streets and local
OL,21,Fbusinesses.
