OL,7,F"This Government's plan for change
OL,8,Fwill put money back in people's
OL,9,Fpockets, with this new remit marking
OL,10,Fthe next step in considering how we
OL,11,Fensure a fair deal for our lowest-paid
OL,12,Fworkers while maintaining a
OL,13,Fcompetitive economy that boosts
OL,14,Fbusinesses and their employees alike."
OL,16,FBaroness Philippa Stroud, chairwoman
OL,17,Fof the LPC, said: "We are pleased to
OL,18,Freceive our remit from the Government.
